OL,3,CGang busted for allegedly smuggling
OL,4,C40,000 stolen phones to China
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police released this
OL,7,Fvideo of thieves snatching handsets
OL,8,Ffrom unsuspecting pedestrians
OL,10,FA major criminal network suspected of
OL,11,Fsmuggling up to 40,000 stolen phones
OL,12,Ffrom the UK to China over the past 12
OL,13,Fmonths has been dismantled by police.
OL,15,FIn the UK's largest crackdown on
OL,16,Fmobile thefts, the Metropolitan Police
OL,17,Fhas arrested 46 people after a months-
OL,18,Flong investigation.
