OL,3,CGang busted for allegedly smuggling
OL,4,C40,000 stolen phones to China
OL,6,FLast December, a box containing around
OL,7,F1,000 stolen iPhones that were
OL,8,Fprepared to be shipped to Hong Kong
OL,9,Fwas found at a warehouse near Heathrow
OL,10,FAirport, according to the force.
OL,12,FIn September, two men, aged in their
OL,13,F30s, were arrested in north-east
OL,14,FLondon and charged on suspicion of
OL,15,Fhandling stolen goods.
OL,17,FA number of phones were found in their
OL,18,Fcar and around 2,000 more devices were
OL,19,Ffound at properties linked to the
OL,20,Fsuspects, the Met added.
