OL,3,CGang busted for allegedly smuggling
OL,4,C40,000 stolen phones to China
OL,6,FThe operation uncovered details of
OL,7,Fsome of the street-level offenders
OL,8,Finvolved in thefts and robberies.
OL,10,FThe group reportedly targeted Apple
OL,11,Fproducts because of their
OL,12,Fprofitability overseas.
OL,14,FStreet thieves were being paid up to
OL,15,F#300 per handset and uncovered
OL,16,Fevidence of devices being sold for up
OL,17,Fto $5,000 USD (#3,700) in China.
