OL,3,CGang busted for allegedly smuggling
OL,4,C40,000 stolen phones to China
OL,6,FOver the last week, 15 more people
OL,7,Fhave been arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Ftheft, handling stolen goods and
OL,9,Fconspiracy to steal.
OL,11,FA total of 46 people have been
OL,12,Farrested across two weeks of what the
OL,13,FMet describes as "targeted and precise
OL,14,Factivity".
