OL,3,CGang busted for allegedly smuggling
OL,4,C40,000 stolen phones to China
OL,6,FThese include 11 arrests made during
OL,7,Fan operation targeting criminal gangs
OL,8,Frobbing courier vans delivering the
OL,9,Fnew iPhone 17 and two men who were
OL,10,Farrested on suspicion of money
OL,11,Flaundering and handling stolen goods
OL,12,Fafter approximately #40,000 in cash
OL,13,Fwas recovered at a phone shop in
OL,14,FIslington.
OL,16,FAnother man was charged with handling
OL,17,Fstolen goods after being stopped with
OL,18,F10 suspected stolen phones at Heathrow
OL,19,FAirport last month.
