OL,6,FFurther enquiries found the same man
OL,7,Fhad travelled between London and
OL,8,FAlgeria more than 200 times in two
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FCommander Andrew Featherstone, the
OL,12,FMet's lead for tackling phone theft,
OL,13,Fdescribed it as the "largest crackdown
OL,14,Fon mobile phone theft and robbery in
OL,15,Fthe UK".
