OL,3,CGang busted for allegedly smuggling
OL,4,C40,000 stolen phones to China
OL,6,FHe added: "We've dismantled criminal
OL,7,Fnetworks at every level, from street-
OL,8,Flevel thieves to international
OL,9,Forganised crime groups exporting tens
OL,10,Fof thousands of stolen devices each
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,F"We've shown how serious we are about
OL,14,Ftackling this issue, but we need more
OL,15,Fhelp from the industry. We're calling
OL,16,Fon phone manufacturers such as Apple
OL,17,Fand Samsung to do more to support us
OL,18,Fand protect their customers
OL,19,F-especially around phone security and
OL,20,Fre-use."
